Battery (9V)

### Links we looked at
- https://docs.arduino.cc/hardware/motor-shield-rev3/ (Arduino motor shield)
- https://www.st.com/resource/en/datasheet/l298.pdf (Popular H-bridge IC used in motor shield)
- Mediapipe/OpenCV (For AI object recognition)
- https://coretecrobotics.co.uk/products/tiny-4wd-robot-kit (Personal 4-wheel robot I have at home for testing. Can have camera mounted)
- https://control.ros.org/rolling/doc/ros2_controllers/doc/mobile_robot_kinematics.html#differential-drive-robot (Kinematic Analysis - 2 wheel robot)
- https://link.springer.com/book/10.1007/978-1-84628-642-1 (Textbook reference for Kinematics)
- https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dead_reckoning (Dead Reckoning concept)
- Omni/mechanum wheels (Allow for side-to-side movement, mechanum can go diagonal)
